ns1:Requirement.ns1:Description:
[In Response Body] The response body is JSON (as specified in [RFC4627]) with the following parameters:
JSON:
 {
 "Name":{"type":"string","optional":false}
 }

[In Response Body] The response body is JSON (as specified in [RFC4627]) with the following parameters:
JSON:
 {
 "Children":
   [{
     "Name":"<name>",
     "Url":"<url>",
     "Version":"<version>"
    }],
 }
